  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2978780/extras/e02b8ef09d5fb1d5cd23cfb7775b0638.avif?t=1751785325\" width=616 height=72 /></span>After school, when a heavy rain that never stops falling makes it difficult for the students to go home</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The relationship between the two, who were spending the day in the club room</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The relationship between the two of them in the club room was shortened after that day...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2978780/extras/7560d530a56e92094a4297ea085e2f60.avif?t=1751785325\" width=616 height=72 /></span>With a classmate and a quiet girlfriend.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Conversations and chats on the way to school</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Messages during class</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Calls before bedtime</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can experience a simulated school life with these interactions!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2978780/extras/af1a1d64c1a17acc9a6b3e9094868cbe.avif?t=1751785325\" width=616 height=72 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2978780/extras/2169e0de67d8432c3c0b3c405783ddc6.avif?t=1751785325\" width=616 height=462 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2978780/extras/dde0d62eb3be0af6faf566a2fc9e4035.avif?t=1751785325\" width=616 height=72 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Heroine who keeps moving by Live2D</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　Conversation part where facial expressions change</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2978780/extras/b63ed1ef245b6ac07f2c28b7ba974b5a.poster.avif?t=1751785325\" width=800 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2978780/extras/b63ed1ef245b6ac07f2c28b7ba974b5a.webm?t=1751785325\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2978780/extras/b63ed1ef245b6ac07f2c28b7ba974b5a.mp4?t=1751785325\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>　Because this work uses Live2D</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　Except for some event stills</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　When the heroine appears on the screen</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　The animation will continue to play.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Daily life with her classmate</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　Before going to school, you can communicate with her via a messaging app.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2978780/extras/747910726e3ac402611ecfbf5b9af108.poster.avif?t=1751785325\" width=800 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2978780/extras/747910726e3ac402611ecfbf5b9af108.webm?t=1751785325\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2978780/extras/747910726e3ac402611ecfbf5b9af108.mp4?t=1751785325\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>　Chatting with her before HR</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　Messaging her secretly during class</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　Spending recess together</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　Sending messages before bedtime</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　Falling asleep while talking</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　You can spend such a common day with her in a relaxed atmosphere.</p>",
